    "AI evolves over a path of maturity spanning a continuum of contemporary cognitive architectures to more socio-cognitive and cross-domain architectures (e.g., Gupta et al., 2023), and in terms of implementation and human-centricity, needs to be interpreted in the context of place and time (Wilkens et al., 2021a)."
